<taxonomicName id="6AFD76B1749687754F459A92132FF539" authorityName="Efetov &amp; Hofmann &amp; Tarmann &amp; Tremewan" authorityYear="2014" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. aurargentea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" status="stat. rev." subSpecies="aurargentea">Zygaena rhadamanthus aurargentea</taxonomicName>
Mazel, 1979, Entomops, Nice 6: 267, figs 1, 2 (
<taxonomicName id="04C4D17B88E3EB6781AB9778BFEA2013" authorityName="Efetov &amp; Hofmann &amp; Tarmann &amp; Tremewan" authorityYear="2014" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="stat. rev.">Zygaena</taxonomicName>
). Type-locality. France: 
<normalizedToken id="D693B39A9921685C4CC3610DDC685671" originalValue="Pyrénées-Orientales">Pyrenees-Orientales</normalizedToken>
, Coustouges.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="301D7DD6CF019BE5F2EF242F7B4FB9A8" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="128" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" type="distribution and taxonomic notes">
<paragraph id="4E3BCF3A5CAB5568376EDFEA1DF25A9B" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">Distribution and taxonomic notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AD80ACDFF104B29F24D0559FE55E45B9" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="128" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">
Described from Coustouges (
<normalizedToken id="30D47BD4C07140373908A53821193B52" originalValue="Pyrénées-Orientales">Pyrenees-Orientales</normalizedToken>
, France), 
<taxonomicName id="F448C96D9F6D7002821A2A87159A150F" authorityName="Efetov &amp; Hofmann &amp; Tarmann &amp; Tremewan" authorityYear="2014" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. aurargentea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="128" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="aurargentea">
<emphasis id="161FFFC7B075E5E202DCE972570EDEF9" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="128">
<pageBreakToken id="541F258DDBDAB8641C5D756B1FF24ABE" pageId="5" pageNumber="128" start="start">Zygaena</pageBreakToken>
rhadamanthus aurargentea
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is also found in Spain (Barcelona and Gerona, excluding coastal regions). It is distinguished from 
<taxonomicName id="087E052CD314F93BF61E07448E23A50E" authority="rhadamanthus" authorityName="rhadamanthus (Esper" authorityYear="1789" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. rhadamanthus" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="128" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="rhadamanthus">
<emphasis id="021139246B8221A61924628F574848A2" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="128">Zygaena rhadamanthus rhadamanthus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the extreme griseoid phenotype, i.e. with pronounced white scaling on the ground colour of the forewings, especially in the females, which is reminiscent of 
<taxonomicName id="BEE7FFA4E41C8072E432DBAB7D86C490" authorityName="Oberthuer" authorityYear="1909" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. grisea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="128" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="grisea">
<emphasis id="185D81650E6C51FEA40FF13ED5E5B2A7" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="128">Zygaena rhadamanthus grisea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from south-eastern and southern-central France (see above), and by the presence of a strong abdominal cingulum that is also present ventrally. 
<bibRefCitation id="5C23B97125B7B6142D96C73E09B64212" author="Leraut, P" journalOrPublisher="NAP Editions, Verrieres-le Buisson" pageId="7" pageNumber="130" refId="B20" refString="Leraut, P, 2012. Volume 3: Moths of Europe, Zygaenids, Pyralids 1 and Brachodids. NAP Editions, Verrieres-le Buisson" title="Volume 3: Moths of Europe, Zygaenids, Pyralids 1 and Brachodids." year="2012">Leraut (2012</bibRefCitation>
: 98) placed 
<taxonomicName id="8961A2B8B0B8EB50CB8E5381A824987C" authorityName="Efetov &amp; Hofmann &amp; Tarmann &amp; Tremewan" authorityYear="2014" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. aurargentea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="128" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="aurargentea">
<emphasis id="12F9F4907E8689BD8DA10DEB4CBF3796" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="128">Zygaena rhadamanthus aurargentea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="12822638898FAA5F993DC4DF5F1C7D6C" authorityName="Dujardin" authorityYear="1956" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. cleui" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="128" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="cleui">
<emphasis id="F4FE6899038F6C973A72B7DB06E17CE7" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="128">Zygaena rhadamanthus cleui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which he reinstated as a valid subspecies, but we see no justification for this (see also above). The former is here reinstated (
<emphasis id="9C8A93FAF5A7427B081CFBF5525E18F5" bold="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="128">stat. rev.</emphasis>
) as a valid subspecies, based on its extreme phenotype, which is so strongly different from that of the nominotypical taxon 
<taxonomicName id="7B181EF10561F04F5FE87C3A6381075E" authority="rhadamanthus" authorityName="rhadamanthus (Esper" authorityYear="1789" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. rhadamanthus" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="128" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="rhadamanthus">
<emphasis id="8319428A3E098813E01783CFFF58AA0C" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="128">Zygaena rhadamanthus rhadamanthus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="2C1038A90408C81FE728C7245BD29760" author="Hofmann, A" journalOrPublisher="Harley Books, Colchester" pageId="7" pageNumber="130" refId="B17" refString="Hofmann, A, Tremewan, WG, 1996. A systematic Catalogue of the Zygaeninae (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae). Harley Books, Colchester" title="A systematic Catalogue of the Zygaeninae (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae)." year="1996">Hofmann and Tremewan 1996</bibRefCitation>
: 131).
</paragraph>
